Package: conditionr
Type: Package
Title: Custom R conditions
Version: 0.1.4
Date: 2014-09-30 21:30:31
Author: Janko Thyson [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Janko Thyson <janko.thyson@gmail.com>
Description: Allows the creation of custom condition classes and thus the use
        of more complex/informative condition objects and messages for which
        appropriate handler methods can be written.
